sequenceDiagram
    title Consumer-Driven Contract Testing

    participant Consumer as Consumer Service
    participant MockAPI as api-mock-service
    participant Spec as OpenAPI Spec / YAML Scenarios

    note over Consumer,Spec: Setup Phase
    Spec ->> MockAPI: Upload spec or YAML scenarios
    MockAPI -->> Spec: Scenarios generated (one per variant)

    note over Consumer,MockAPI: Test Execution Phase
    Consumer ->> MockAPI: Send request with test data
    MockAPI ->> MockAPI: Match scenario (path + headers + body)
    MockAPI ->> MockAPI: Render template response\n(body fields → {{.fieldName}} auto-injected)

    alt Request matches scenario
        MockAPI -->> Consumer: Return mock response
        Consumer ->> Consumer: Assert response shape\n(JSONPath assertions: $.user.email)
        Consumer ->> Consumer: Validate contract expectations
    else No matching scenario
        MockAPI -->> Consumer: 404 / fallback response
        Consumer ->> Consumer: Assert error handling
    end

    note over Consumer,MockAPI: Results
    Consumer ->> Consumer: Record test pass/fail
    Consumer ->> Consumer: Consumer contract verified
